<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Garland" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Garland,</orth> 1) a wreath, chaplet: <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. IV, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 196</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 196</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.73" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.228" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 228</bibl>, <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.333" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 333</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 138</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 5.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. V, 3, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.169" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 2, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 11</bibl>. Emblem of glory: <cit><quote>call kim noble that was now your hate, him vile that was your g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.188" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 188</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Marcius wears this war's g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.9.60" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 9, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he lurched all swords of the g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.105" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>withered is the g. of the war,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.15.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 15, 64</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) the crown: <cit><quote>so thou the g. wearest successively,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.202" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 5, 202</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.84" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 2, 40</bibl>
